WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:04.080
Barclays Online Banking.
How to make a transfer.

2
00:00:07.720 --> 00:00:12.920
It's easy to make a transfer with Online
Banking between your Barclays accounts.

3
00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:16.160
From the homepage, click on 'Transfer'.

4
00:00:16.360 --> 00:00:19.080
Select the account you want to make
the transfer from

5
00:00:19.480 --> 00:00:22.560
and the account you want
to make the transfer to.

6
00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:25.960
Next enter the amount you'd like

7
00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:32.320
to transfer and choose when you'd like to
make the transfer, now or at a later date.

8
00:00:32.520 --> 00:00:35.600
Then add a reference for the transfer

9
00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:39.720
before clicking on 'Check
and confirm details'.

10
00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:42.840
Scroll down to check through your details

11
00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:46.840
and if you're happy,
click 'Confirm transfer'.

12
00:00:47.040 --> 00:00:48.560
And there you are -

13
00:00:48.760 --> 00:00:50.400
your transfer will be made.

